## Data Model

All models are in `pkg/controller/provider/model/ovirt/model.go`.

### Base Fields (all resources)

```
ID          string    (primary key — oVirt UUID)
Name        string    (indexed)
Description string
Revision    int64     (auto-incremented, indexed)
```

